---

<Layout title="About Us">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative h-[70vh] overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-black/70 to-black/50 z-10"></div>
    <video 
      class="absolute w-full h-full object-cover"
      autoplay 
      loop 
      muted 
      playsinline
    >
      <source src="https://player.vimeo.com/external/517629306.hd.mp4?s=b0bea37ef4b0a29d6b291b6d2584d81ffb305f1d&profile_id=175" type="video/mp4">
    </video>
    
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-20 flex items-center">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 font-display leading-tight">
            Our Story
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-cream-light leading-relaxed">
            From a student's vision at the Air Force Institute of Technology to a movement transforming Africa's relationship with plastics.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Origin Story Section -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <SectionHeading 
            title="The Birth of Terra Verte Afrika" 
            subtitle="How a personal journey became a continental movement"
          />
          
          <div class="prose prose-lg prose-green">
            <p>
              Terra Verte Afrika began in the halls of the Air Force Institute of Technology, where I witnessed firsthand the overwhelming presence of plastic waste on our campus. As an environmental engineering student, I was struck by the disconnect between our academic discussions of sustainability and the reality of our daily practices.
            </p>
            
            <p>
              The name "Terra Verte Afrika" combines Latin and Swahili influences - "Terra Verte" meaning "Green Earth" and "Afrika" representing our continent's unique spelling - symbolizing our commitment to blend traditional African wisdom with modern environmental solutions.
            </p>
            
            <blockquote class="italic text-green-dark border-l-4 border-green pl-4 my-6">
              "What started as a campus cleanup initiative has grown into a movement that's transforming how Africa thinks about plastic waste."
            </blockquote>
            
            <p>
              My university education opened my eyes to the scientific reality of plastic pollution, but it was the daily sight of plastic-choked drainage systems during rainy seasons that truly catalyzed action. We started with simple campus cleanup drives, but quickly realized the need for systemic change.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="relative">
          <img 
            src={campusImage} 
            alt="Air Force Institute of Technology campus" 
            class="rounded-lg shadow-xl w-full h-auto"
          />
          <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 bg-green p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg max-w-xs">
            <p class="text-white font-medium italic">
              "Every piece of plastic we remove today is one less threat to tomorrow's Africa."
            </p>
            <p class="text-white font-bold mt-2">- Amina Okafor, Founder</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission & Vision Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-cream-light to-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <SectionHeading 
        title="Our Purpose" 
        subtitle="Guided by clear goals and unwavering values"
        centered={true}
      />
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-12">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-dark mb-4">Mission Statement</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            To eliminate single-use plastics across Africa through education, innovation, and community action, while preserving our cultural heritage and promoting sustainable development.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-dark mb-4">Vision Statement</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            An Africa where communities thrive in harmony with nature, where traditional wisdom meets modern sustainability, and where future generations inherit clean waters and healthy ecosystems.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-dark mb-4">Short-Term Goals</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-green mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Implement plastic-free zones in 50 university campuses</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-green mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Establish student environmental clubs in 200 schools</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-green mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Train 1,000 youth environmental ambassadors</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-dark mb-4">Long-Term Goals</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-green mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Achieve 50% reduction in single-use plastics across major African cities</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-green mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Implement comprehensive plastic policies in 20 African countries</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-green mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Create a continent-wide network of sustainable waste management systems</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Timeline Section -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <SectionHeading 
        title="Our Journey" 
        subtitle="From campus initiative to continental movement"
        centered={true}
      />
      
      <div class="relative mt-12">
        <!-- Timeline Line -->
        <div class="absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 h-full w-1 bg-green"></div>
        
        <!-- Timeline Items -->
        <div class="space-y-12">
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-auto mr-8 md:mr-auto md:ml-8 p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md w-full md:w-[calc(50%-4rem)] transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-green-dark mb-2">2020: The Beginning</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">First campus cleanup drive at Air Force Institute of Technology</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="mr-auto ml-8 md:ml-auto md:mr-8 p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md w-full md:w-[calc(50%-4rem)] transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-green-dark mb-2">2021: Expansion</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Launched pilot programs in 5 Nigerian universities</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-auto mr-8 md:mr-auto md:ml-8 p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md w-full md:w-[calc(50%-4rem)] transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-green-dark mb-2">2022: Recognition</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Won the African Environmental Innovation Award</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="mr-auto ml-8 md:ml-auto md:mr-8 p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md w-full md:w-[calc(50%-4rem)] transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-green-dark mb-2">2023: Continental Growth</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Expanded to 10 African countries with 50+ partner organizations</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>



  <!-- Impact Section -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <SectionHeading 
        title="Our Impact" 
        subtitle="Measurable change we've created across Africa"
        centered={true}
      />
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-12">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md text-center transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-green mb-2">500M+</div>
          <div class="text-xl text-gray-700">Plastic items prevented</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md text-center transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-green mb-2">25+</div>
          <div class="text-xl text-gray-700">Communities engaged</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md text-center transform hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-green mb-2">10K+</div>
          <div class="text-xl text-gray-700">Volunteers mobilized</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-green text-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 font-display">Join Our Movement</h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Be part of the solution to create a plastic-free Africa. Together, we can make a lasting impact for generations to come.
      </p>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <Button href="/get-involved" variant="outline" size="lg">Volunteer With Us</Button>
        <Button href="/donate" variant="secondary" size="lg">Support Our Work</Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>